
The Prosperity Passport is a Web3 identity solution that allows users to mint various SBTs tied to their on-chain and off-chain reputation. These tokens include:

User Verification SBT – Confirms your identity.
Credit Score SBT – Reflects your financial behavior.
Community Reputation SBT – Measures your engagement and trustworthiness.
.celo Domain Name SBT – A unique identifier for your Web3 presence.

These tokens are stored in your wallet and cannot be transferred, making them ideal for building a trustworthy digital identity.
